                                                    semper suscipit, posuere a, pede. Donec nec justo eget felis
                                                    facilisis fermentum.
                                                </div><!-- End .card-body -->
                                            </div><!-- End .collapse -->
                                        </div><!-- End .card -->

                                        <div class="card">
                                            <div class="card-header" id="heading-5">
                                                <h2 class="card-title">
                                                    <input class="collapsed" name="payment" value="razorPay" type="radio" data-toggle="collapse"
                                                        href="#collapse-5" aria-expanded="false"
                                                        aria-controls="collapse-5">
                                                        Razor Pay
                                                        <img src="assets/images/payments-summary.png"
                                                            alt="payments cards">
                                                    </a>
                                                </h2>
                                            </div><!-- End .card-header -->
                                            <div id="collapse-5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading-5"
                                                data-parent="#accordion-payment">
                                                <div class="card-body"> Donec nec justo eget felis facilisis
